     <paramdef>bool <parameter>radio</parameter></paramdef>
    </funcprototype>
   </funcsynopsis>
   <shortdesc>
    Sets the style of the toggle button. If true, the toggle will be shown as RadioButton.
   </shortdesc>
   <desc>
    <para>
     Sets the style of the toggle button. If radio is TRUE, the cell renderer
     renders a radio toggle. If FALSE, it renders a check toggle.
    </para>
    <para>
     See also: 
     <function class="GtkCellRendererToggle">get_radio</function>
